  <name>get_iplayer</name>
  <summary>Download programmes from BBC iPlayer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      get_iplayer allows you to download BBC television and radio
      programmes for later viewing and listening.
    </p>
    <p>
      With get_iplayer installed, click the "Download" links on the BBC
      iPlayer website to download programmes to your computer, or use
      the command line.
    </p>
  </description>
